PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779369077
OL,3,CFashion student creates clothing line
OL,4,Cfor autistic children with sensory
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FA fashion student has created a line
OL,8,Fof clothes for children with autism
OL,9,Fwho may struggle with sensory overload.
OL,11,FFarah Conn, who is in her final year
OL,12,Fof fashion technology at Heriot-Watt
OL,13,FUniversity, has invented her own brand
OL,14,Fof seaside-inspired garments that have
OL,15,Fultra-soft fabrics, flattened seams
OL,16,Fand are label-free.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779369077
OL,3,CFashion student creates clothing line
OL,4,Cfor autistic children with sensory
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FDubbed Little Waves, Ms Conn's
OL,8,Fcollection is for children aged three
OL,9,Fto 12, and will later be featured at
OL,10,Fher university's school of textiles
OL,11,Fand design at its Borders campus,
OL,12,FGalashiels.
OL,14,FThe student, who comes from Biggar,
OL,15,FSouth Lanarkshire, was inspired by
OL,16,Fparents, carers and professionals who
OL,17,Fsupport children with autism.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779369077
OL,3,CFashion student creates clothing line
OL,4,Cfor autistic children with sensory
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FFarah said: "Fashion technology is
OL,8,Fabout solving real problems. I didn't
OL,9,Funderstand why children with autism
OL,10,Fshould have fewer choices or less
OL,11,Fexciting clothing.
OL,13,F"I wanted to design garments that were
OL,14,Fcalming and functional, but also
OL,15,Fjoyful and inclusive, something
OL,16,Fchildren could feel good wearing.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779369077
OL,3,CFashion student creates clothing line
OL,4,Cfor autistic children with sensory
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"Through my own experiences speaking
OL,8,Fwith parents and professionals, it
OL,9,Fbecame really clear to me that a lot
OL,10,Fof clothing available for autistic
OL,11,Fchildren simply isn't designed with
OL,12,Ftheir needs or their individuality in
OL,13,Fmind.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779369077
OL,3,CFashion student creates clothing line
OL,4,Cfor autistic children with sensory
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"I wanted to solve a real problem and
OL,8,Fcreate garments that support sensory
OL,9,Fcomfort while still being fun,
OL,10,Finclusive and empowering. Autistic
OL,11,Fchildren deserve the same
OL,12,Fopportunities to feel confident and
OL,13,Fexcited about what they wear as any
OL,14,Fother child."
OL,16,FShe added: "I'm incredibly proud to be
OL,17,Fpresenting this work and to have had
OL,18,Fthe opportunity to explore how fashion
OL,19,Fcan make a genuine difference to
OL,20,Fpeople's everyday lives.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779369077
OL,3,CFashion student creates clothing line
OL,4,Cfor autistic children with sensory
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"This project means a lot to me, and I
OL,8,Fhope it can be developed further after
OL,9,FI graduate this summer, whether that's
OL,10,Fthrough industry collaboration,
OL,11,Ffurther research or eventually
OL,12,Fbecoming something that families can
OL,13,Faccess more widely. I'd love to
OL,14,Fcontinue working in inclusive design
OL,15,Fand carry this approach forward into
OL,16,Fmy career."
OL,18,FBruce Roberts, global head of fashion
OL,19,Fand textiles at Heriot-Watt
OL,20,FUniversity, helped Ms Conn throughout
OL,21,Fher project.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779369077
OL,3,CFashion student creates clothing line
OL,4,Cfor autistic children with sensory
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FHe said: "Farah's project is an
OL,8,Fexcellent example of what fashion
OL,9,Ftechnology at HeriotWatt is about `
OL,10,Fthoughtful, researchled design that
OL,11,Fresponds to real human needs.
OL,13,F"She approached this work with
OL,14,Fsensitivity, rigour and a clear sense
OL,15,Fof purpose, drawing on user insight
OL,16,Fand technical knowledge to create
OL,17,Fsomething genuinely innovative.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779369077
OL,3,CFashion student creates clothing line
OL,4,Cfor autistic children with sensory
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"It has been a privilege to support
OL,8,Fher through the process and see the
OL,9,Fconfidence and clarity she's developed
OL,10,Fas a designer."
OL,12,FMs Conn's work is one of 90 projects
OL,13,Fto be showcased at the university's
OL,14,Ftextile and design degree show, which
OL,15,Fis open from Saturday, May 23-30 and
OL,16,Fis free to attend.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
